title: One of the year's Lousiest films!
review: I've seen more interesting things written on bathroom walls.The most interesting part of this film was the cool toys John Lovitz character owned.Rob Schneider hit a new all time low on this one, and that's saying something.I didn't think Napolean Dynamite could do worse than his original, I was wrong...It wasn't a really bad movie, until the end when it all comes together to make a point and have a moral behind the story...The best part was the credits rolling.
